These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, blend
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, d&b
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Cigar      | blend     | bluemaster |
| Transport   | scooter | skateboard      |
| Music-Genre         | d&b    | trance      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, jazz
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, car
1. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Nationality         | brazilian      | pakistani |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | dubstep    |
| Transport           | car         | bus         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, cricket
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Sport         | surfing | cricket |
| Hobby         | writing       | collecting       |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | disco         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, paramedic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, superhero
2 different pets are kept: turtle, frog
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Job    | paramedic    | designer     |
| Movie-Genre       | satire    | superhero |
| Pet   | turtle | frog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, argentine
City: miami, liverpool
1. the argentine is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the indian is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Flower       | daffodil | balloon-flower |
| Nationality         | indian      | argentine  |
| City   | miami | liverpool   |

